<div class="flex flex-col min-h-[100dvh] dark:bg-background dark:text-card-foreground">
  <main class="flex-1">
    <section class="w-full py-12 md:py-24 lg:py-32 bg-muted dark:bg-card">
      <div class="container grid items-center justify-center gap-4 px-4 text-center md:px-6 lg:gap-10">
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <h1 class="text-3xl dark:text-blue-400 font-bold tracking-tighter sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl">VISI KAMI</h1>
          <p class="mx-auto dark:text-white max-w-[700px] text-muted-foreground dark:text-card-foreground md:text-xl/relaxed lg:text-base/relaxed xl:text-xl/relaxed">
          Menjadi perusahaan pengadaan barang dan jasa yang profesional, terpercaya, unggul, dan berkembang dengan meningkatkan kualitas pengelolaan administrasi, sumber daya manusia, serta mewujudkan sistem pengadaan yang kredibel.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="w-full py-12 md:py-24 lg:py-32 dark:bg-background">
      <div class="container grid items-center justify-center gap-4 px-4 text-center md:px-6 lg:gap-10">
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-3xl dark:text-blue-400 font-bold tracking-tighter sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl">MISI KAMI</h2>
          <p class="mx-auto max-w-[700px] text-muted-foreground dark:text-white dark:text-card-foreground md:text-xl/relaxed lg:text-base/relaxed xl:text-xl/relaxed">
            At the heart of our company are the principles that guide our actions and decisions.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center space-y-4 p-6 bg-background dark:bg-card rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#00bfac" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-shield"><path d="M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z"/></svg>
            <h3 class="text-xl dark:text-blue-400 font-bold dark:text-card-foreground">Menjaga Mutu</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground dark:text-white dark:text-card-foreground text-center">
                Memberikan kepercayaan kepada konsumen baik dalam kualitas maupun pelayanan.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center space-y-4 p-6 bg-background dark:bg-card rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#00bfac" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chart-spline"><path d="M3 3v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16"/><path d="M7 16c.5-2 1.5-7 4-7 2 0 2 3 4 3 2.5 0 4.5-5 5-7"/></svg>
