            <p class="text-muted-foreground dark:text-white dark:text-card-foreground text-center">
                Dapat berperan aktif dengan pemerintah maupun swasta dalam mengembangkan usaha untuk pembangunan negara.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center space-y-4 p-6 bg-background dark:bg-card rounded-lg shadow-md">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#00bfac" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-handshake"><path d="m11 17 2 2a1 1 0 1 0 3-3"/><path d="m14 14 2.5 2.5a1 1 0 1 0 3-3l-3.88-3.88a3 3 0 0 0-4.24 0l-.88.88a1 1 0 1 1-3-3l2.81-2.81a5.79 5.79 0 0 1 7.06-.87l.47.28a2 2 0 0 0 1.42.25L21 4"/><path d="m21 3 1 11h-2"/><path d="M3 3 2 14l6.5 6.5a1 1 0 1 0 3-3"/><path d="M3 4h8"/></svg>
            <h3 class="text-xl dark:text-blue-400 font-bold dark:text-card-foreground">Etika Bisnis</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground dark:text-white dark:text-card-foreground text-center">
                Mewujudkan sistem manajemen perusahaan yang menjunjung tinggi etika bisnis dan sosial.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center space-y-4 p-6 bg-background dark:bg-card rounded-lg shadow-md">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#00bfac" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle-dollar-sign"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M16 8h-6a2 2 0 1 0 0 4h4a2 2 0 1 1 0 4H8"/><path d="M12 18V6"/></svg>
